	ntry into the venue once exited. All patrons require a ticket\, regardless
	 of age. Including babies in arms. Lumen Field/WAMU Theater is not respons
	ible for third party ticket purchases. There is an overall six (6) ticket 
	limit for this event. Anyone found purchasing above the set ticket limit m
	ay have partially or their entire refund cancelled. WAMU Theater has a cle
	ar bag policy\, please see our website for specific information.\nRAYE has
	 partnered with PLUS1 so that $1 per ticket supports organizations bringin
