SUMMARY:Free Playwriting Workshop for Veterans & their loved ones
DTSTAMP:20260403T051043Z
DTSTART:20260408T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get your ideas out of your head and onto the page through guide
	d writing exercises. In this workshop\, you’ll learn about foundational el
	ements of playwriting in a beginner-friendly environment where our goal is
	 to have fun and see what we can create.\n\nThis class is designed for wri
	ters of all experience levels. By the end of the course\, you will leave w
	ith new ideas and new ways to build your stories.\n\nASAP classes are free
	 for service members\, veterans\, military spouses\, family members\, care
	givers\, and survivors.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/f
	ree-playwriting-workshop-for-veterans-their-loved-ones/18426721/2026-04-07
